#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:282
msgid ""
"The Hours Calculator is a comprehensive tool for calculating time "
"differences, adding or subtracting hours from times, converting between time"
" units (hours, minutes, seconds, days), calculating total hours from "
"multiple periods, and calculating hours worked with break time deductions. "
"This calculator is essential for time tracking, scheduling, payroll, and "
"time management."
