"algorithms to analyze name compatibility, including counting letters in "
"'LOVE', finding common letters, comparing name lengths, and analyzing "
"vowel/consonant ratios. While this is primarily for entertainment purposes, "
"it can be a fun way to explore name relationships and compatibility."
